Simulation.name: Calculate the evolution of the Jupiter trojans
Simulation.description: The system consists of the Sun, Jupiter, Saturn as massive bodies and a swarm of real Jupiter trojans around L4. This is a project supervised by Prof. Bálint Érdi.
